name: Orientation. Meteorite I.
description: Image of the meteorite that appears in the first episode of the Prom Trilogy (Orientation/Induction/Launch) broadcasted by Radial Gallery (Madrid, New York) where we combined our interests for science fiction and party cultures. In this series of transmissions we drew on fleeting images and notions around the ideas of space exploration, health and the new folk knowledge of allegedly scientific genetic studies. https://vimeo.com/255944398
